# Gunpoint, with Flydigi Apex 2 in mind.

JoyXY wasd deadzone 40 # Movement
CamXY mouse 100 # Move mouse
mousecalibration 900
ingamemouse 1.0

TriggerR M1 # Click
BumperR M2 # Right Click
TriggerL M2 # Cancel / Draw Gun
BumperL Alt # Crosslink

ActionH 1 # Option 1
ActionV 2 # Option 2
ActionB 3 # Option 3
ActionA Space # Accept
ActionC R # Restart

MenuL Tab
MenuR Escape

DpadXY arrows # Pan Camera
